short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: Brings back the freedom of launching your favorite homepage even on stubborn mobile browsers.
short.de: Bringt die Freiheit zurück, Ihre Lieblings-Homepage auch auf hartnäckigen mobilen Browsern zu starten.
short.es,es_419: Trae de vuelta la libertad de lanzar su página de inicio favorita, incluso en los navegadores móviles obstinados.
short.fr: Ramène la liberté de lancer votre page d’accueil préférée, même sur les navigateurs mobiles tenaces.
short.it: Riporta la libertà di lanciare la tua homepage preferita anche su browser mobili testardi.
short.ja: 頑固なモバイルブラウザでも、お気に入りのホームページを自由に起動できます。
short.pt_BR,pt_PT: Traz de volta a liberdade de lançar sua página inicial favorita, mesmo em navegadores móveis teimosos.
short.ru: Вернет свободу запуска Вашей любимой домашней страницы даже в упрямых мобильных браузерах.
short.zh_CN,zh_TW: 带回你最喜欢的主页，即使是在顽固的手机浏览器上。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
📱 YOU'LL BE ABLE TO:
➕ Add the Open SwiftDial button on all websites
🖼️ Choose position, size, color and opacity of the button
➕ Open a new tab with SwiftDial on browser startup
➕ Replace the active tab with SwiftDial on browser startup

📝 NOTES:
✔️ Works with SwiftDial 49 and newer.
✔️ This Launcher version is generally intended for browsers without standard support for homepage extensions, like Yandex Browser, but can also be used with normal browsers.
☝️ Some features might not be supported by some browsers.
☝️ If you're using the SwiftDial YN variant, you need to choose it in the Launcher settings.

➕ LEARN MORE ABOUT SWIFTDIAL:
SwiftDial is a modern, easily customizable and privacy friendly speed dial | home page | new tab for your browser.
🌐 https://nscript.ru/swiftdial

🎨 CHECK OUT OTHER SWIFTDIAL EXTRAS:
🌐 https://nscript.ru/swiftdial/extras

☝️ Wenn Sie die SwiftDial YN-Variante verwenden, müssen Sie sie in den Launcher-Einstellungen auswählen.
